Package com.w2.api.engine.events

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RobotDeviceEvent
    An interface to represent events for unconnected robots.
    RobotEvent
    An interface for all events related to a specific Robot.
    W2Event
    Marker interface for all W2 events.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EventBusFactory
    The app wide event bus factory which maintains event buses used to publish events related to robot connections and robot specific events.
    RobotCommandSetSequenceActivity
    Abstract base class for the "Stopped" and "Finished" notifications for the 'CommandSetSequence'
    RobotCommandSetSequenceFinished
    This is an event which indicates that a given 'CommandSetSequence' was successfully executed on the robot
    RobotCommandSetSequenceStopped
    This is an event which indicates that a given 'CommandSetSequence' executing on a robot was stopped.
    RobotScannedEvent
    Event indicating that a 'Robot' has been scanned
    RobotSensorSetUpdated
    Event indicating that a robot experienced an update to it's internal state.
